				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Reaction AD to any other guard or Tusgront being killed - mostly to cover edge cases so players know that they'll be attacked on sight. (Only one will play, but all the guards need them incase the player wipes anywhere from 1 to all-bar-one out) - This guard is repeatedly failing to cast a spell normally, so figured I'd give him a bit of flavour."
				}
